<h1>Scrabble Score Calculator</h1>

<p>Find out how many points your word is worth in Scrabble.  Submit your word and we will tell you how much you scored!</p>

<form action='/calculator' method='get'>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="word">Word</label>
    <input id="word" name="word" class="form-control" type="text">
  </div>
  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-info">Score my word</button>
</form>
